race.description: Happy New Year To All Maiden Plate
race.comment: EXCELBOOM (7) hails from the top Tony Gollan stable, and after making a bright start to this season, the wheels have dropped off in her last couple of starts. She will find this easier, and with the aid of a good draw, she will be hard to hold out. SOLAR SURFER (3) was only bloused out in the last stride at Warwick 2 weeks ago and was tying up after the race, which may have cost him the win. He faces a similar field and can go one better. RADIO WAVES (13) will be peaking third up, and he is worth including in all combinations, especially from a decent gate. APOLLO MOON (5) gelding by Anders from Cara De Luna on debut. Ran third at recent trial. Watch for any market confidence.
